{"tid":2215453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《理大圍城》再受打壓 送審DVD遭碎屍  崔允信︰荒謬事一單接一單","createTime":"2020-09-24T04:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:44:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a8857f63cda4a09556d95f2ad8bfe848bad50d","tid":2215453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/MK6Y72FMBBFFHLNKGN52PYLYAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FMK6Y72FMBBFFHLNKGN52PYLYAY%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=78a9c668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FMK6Y72FMBBFFHLNKGN52PYLYAY%2F&h=72e10e8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/MK6Y72FMBBFFHLNKGN52PYLYAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《理大圍城》再受打壓 送審DVD遭碎屍 <br />\n崔允信︰荒謬事一單接一單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ejtGZ3ThAVoSumeK2tEqZh5Kj1k=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QQGZOMO6GBA77AXAF3RNBSOI3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FejtGZ3ThAVoSumeK2tEqZh5Kj1k%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQQGZOMO6GBA77AXAF3RNBSOI3Y.jpg&h=69627d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■崔允信認為連串事件收窄電影創作和觀賞的自由。<br />\n<br />\n獨立紀錄片電影《理大圍城》被電檢處連番留難，發行商「影意志影院」昨凌晨表示，電檢處退還的送審DVD光碟成為「理大碎片」，對事件極為震驚，疑有電檢處員工「有意或無意損壞光碟」，處方未有道歉，僅賠償一隻全新DVD了事。影意志藝術總監崔允信明言難以揣測事發經過，他認為連串事件收窄電影創作和觀賞的自由，更不諱言「過咗呢單，又會有另一單荒謬嘅嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：前檢片顧問︰片頭加警告聞所未聞<br />\n<br />\n由香港紀錄片工作者執導的紀錄片《理大圍城》，本周一起一連三天於香港藝術中心古天樂電影院上映，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電檢處無道歉 僅賠空白光碟<br />\n<br />\n崔允信受訪時強調，電影首天放映時未得悉被退還的光碟成碎片，「嗰日趕住開場，同事只係話光碟爛咗，我以為崩咗或者花咗」。及後同事打開信封，眾人傳來「嘩！」一聲，才發現光碟「碎屍」，「就算用手拗都唔會碎到咁，一忽大一忽細。」他笑說需以能切碎光碟的「碎紙機」才能辦到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QoJx6WbMh_1pjpacMND7oizagIU=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ABFKKLYALBDYBBOKJ34UNLDWFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQoJx6WbMh_1pjpacMND7oizagIU%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FABFKKLYALBDYBBOKJ34UNLDWFM.jpg&h=9ec5b709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《理大圍城》記錄了去年11月理大內外連場驚心動魄的衝突。影意志提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NQjjs-NF5BQWEz_FPN5OoVYIyEg=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QAJH55NEXVEATJERYHBNQ3HJGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNQjjs-NF5BQWEz_FPN5OoVYIyEg%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQAJH55NEXVEATJERYHBNQ3HJGA.jpg&h=2f45c54a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■獨立紀錄片《理大圍城》被電檢處連番留難。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b7S4goD232XsvVGcRUt7QrSE93c=/1181x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VHMG23EZR5DZHO4X4Y57WLGLKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb7S4goD232XsvVGcRUt7QrSE93c%3D%2F1181x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVHMG23EZR5DZHO4X4Y57WLGLKM.jpg&h=c91f2b5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■送審《理大圍城》光碟離奇粉碎，電檢處未有道歉，僅賠全新DVD了事。影意志fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n電檢處沒有向影意志解釋事件，崔允信亦難作揣測，「第一個反應係笑！」其團隊不解為何有人要毀碟，亦坦言光碟不算貴重，現時不過失去一個複本，惟電檢處一直沒正式道歉，只附上另一空白光碟當作「賠償」。<br />\n<br />\n回顧《理大圍城》及《佔領立法會》兩部紀錄片送檢以來的爭議，崔允信指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「你要人加呢個警告，似係個指引，教觀眾應該點樣睇、點解理解呢套戲。」更擔心這些「指引」會延伸至不同獨立電影片種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「再極權之地，都有獨立電影」<br />\n<br />\n從事獨立電影發行多年，崔感慨「過咗呢單，又會有另一單荒謬嘅嘢，好似近日又改記者定義。」他感謝社會關注事件，同時坦言獨立電影生存空間狹小，「《十年》已經係咁，逢親同政治有關嘅片好多戲院唔敢上。」<br />\n<br />\n《理大圍城》放映三場反應熱烈，崔允信說：「起碼賣到幾百萬（票房），一定收得好過唔少本土電影。」。。。。。。。。。。，「再極權嘅地方，就算係伊朗、中國，都有人拍到（獨立）電影。」"},{"pid":"c6f10124388ff694b74569e2b7e4536053f859bc","tid":2215453,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9063ddd4c2aadf2e0e33e924a71b0017268951","tid":2215453,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"好過套麥路人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}